entry.title: Typhoon Haiyan deaths in Philippines passes 6,000 | Fox News
entry.summary:
The death toll from Typhoon Haiyan that struck the central Philippines on Nov. 8
has passed 6000 with nearly 1800 people missing, officials said Friday.
